<div data-stock-sell-calculator>
  <section class="explain-section z-section">
    <h2 class="z-section-title">计算说明</h2>
    <div class="explain-card z-panel">
      <div class="formula-group">
        <span class="formula-label">目标摊薄成本</span>
        <span class="formula-eq">= 每股分红 ÷ 目标股息率</span>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-group">
        <span class="formula-label">卖出价格 P</span>
        <span class="formula-eq">= (持仓总成本 − 剩余份额 × 目标摊薄成本) ÷ 卖出份额</span>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-group">
        <span class="formula-label">盈利比例</span>
        <span class="formula-eq">= (卖出价格 − 买入成本) ÷ 买入成本 × 100%</span>
      </div>
      <p class="explain-note">策略：以高于买入成本的价格卖出部分仓位，利用卖出收益冲减剩余持仓的账面成本，使剩余股票的每股成本下降至目标股息率对应价位。结果仅是数学目标，不构成投资建议。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="input-section z-section">
    <h2 class="z-section-title">参数输入</h2>
    <div class="input-card z-panel">
      <div class="input-grid">
        <div class="input-group z-field">
          <label for="cost">买入成本（元/股）</label>
          <input type="number" id="cost" min="0.01" step="0.01" placeholder="例如 10.00" aria-describedby="calculator-error natural-yield-value" />
        </div>
        <div class="input-group z-field">
          <label for="shares">股票份额（股）</label>
          <input type="number" id="shares" min="1" step="1" placeholder="例如 1000" aria-describedby="calculator-error" />
        </div>
        <div class="input-group z-field">
          <label for="dividend">每股分红（元）</label>
          <input type="number" id="dividend" min="0" step="0.01" placeholder="例如 0.50" aria-describedby="calculator-error natural-yield-value" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="input-insights">
        <div class="natural-yield-card">
          <span class="insight-label">自然股息率</span>
          <strong id="natural-yield-value" class="insight-value">—</strong>
          <span class="insight-note">基于买入成本和每股分红</span>
        </div>
        <div class="assumption-list" aria-label="策略假设">
          <span>100 股为最小卖出单位</span>
          <span>只展示高于买入成本的卖出点</span>
          <span>目标股息率范围 4%–100%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p id="calculator-error" class="calculator-error" role="alert" hidden></p>
      <button id="calc-btn" class="z-btn-primary" type="button">计算卖点</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="table-section z-section" id="result-section" hidden>
    <h2 class="z-section-title">全部可获利卖点</h2>
    <div class="table-wrapper z-table-wrapper">
      <table class="sell-table z-data-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="col-yield">目标股息率</th>
            <th class="col-lots">卖出股数</th>
            <th class="col-price">卖出价格</th>
            <th class="col-cost">目标摊薄成本</th>
            <th class="col-remain">剩余份额</th>
            <th class="col-profit">盈利比例</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="result-body"></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<script>
  import '../../scripts/stock-sell-calculator'
</script>

